da vodi u noćnu šetnjicu?

00:12:40.511 --> 00:12:45.210
Samo se seti... -Šta? -Kolačići.
Možemo se obogatiti od njih.

00:12:45.573 --> 00:12:48.200
Stvarno? Pa, spreman sam na to.

00:12:57.490 --> 00:13:00.190
Stani.

00:13:20.553 --> 00:13:23.253
Hajde, Marvine.

00:13:32.019 --> 00:13:35.017
Stani. Sedi.

00:13:35.785 --> 00:13:40.360
Miran. Hvala ti.

00:14:01.470 --> 00:14:04.906
Ćao, Patersone!
Tačno na vreme. -Ćao, doco.

00:14:06.187 --> 00:14:10.304
